commit.message:
loop-init.c (gate): Do not enale RTL loop unroller with -fpeel-loops.

	* loop-init.c (gate): Do not enale RTL loop unroller with -fpeel-loops.
	It no longer does that.
	* toplev.c (process_options): Do not enable flag_web with -fpeel-loops.

From-SVN: r236915

files.patch:
@@ -1,3 +1,9 @@
+2016-05-31  Jan Hubicka  <hubicka@ucw.cz>
+
+	* loop-init.c (gate): Do not enale RTL loop unroller with -fpeel-loops.
+	It no longer does that.
+	* toplev.c (process_options): Do not enable flag_web with -fpeel-loops.
